rule-4-1-a.test_description: A building has one building segment and one zone with an HVAC system that provides heating and cooling. The zone heating and cooling thermostat schedules match between the baseline and proposed ruleset model descriptions.

standard.rule_description: Temperature Control Setpoints shall be the same for proposed design and baseline building design.

rule-4-1-b.test_description: A building has one building segment and one zone with an HVAC system that provides heating and cooling. The zone heating and cooling thermostat schedules do not match between the baseline and proposed ruleset model descriptions.
rule-4-1-b.expected_raised_message_includes: There is a temperature schedule mismatch between the baseline and proposed RMDs.

standard.rule_description: Temperature Control Setpoints shall be the same for proposed design and baseline building design.
